TION> China </LOCATION> would antagonize the <LOCATION> United </LOCATION> <LOCATION> States </LOCATION>, which has expressed concern about <LOCATION> China </LOCATION>'s sale of silkworm missiles to <LOCATION> Iran </LOCATION>, according to The Sunday Times.
